text:
There are a couple extremely tight tracks in this one still, mostly in the early tracks.
- The vox in 'Soft Collision' adds some catchy, meaty breadth to the track.
- The nice hard swing in 'Soak Patrol Alpha' helps make it distinctly catchy. (and coda's mix is a nice, smooth counterpoint)
- surasshu's mix of 'Tally Screen' is genuinely creepy in a very neat way; even though it's not technically part of the game proper.
